<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Acceso Denegado - Gustarte</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>

  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .error-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 3rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #3498db;
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #2980b9;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #95a5a6;
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #7f8c8d;
    }

    .alert {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: #fff3cd;
      color: #856404;
      border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="error-card">
    <div class="icon">🚫</div>
    <h1>Acceso Denegado</h1>

    <% if alert %>
      <div class="alert"><%= alert %></div>
    <% end %>

    <p>No tienes los permisos necesarios para acceder a esta sección del sistema.</p>
    <p>Solo los administradores y profesores pueden acceder al panel de administración.</p>

    <div>
      <%= link_to "Volver al Inicio", root_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <% if user_signed_in? %>
        <%= button_to "Cerrar Sesión", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "Iniciar Sesión", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
